-- U.K. Stocks Recoup Losses, Leaving FTSE 100 Index Little Changed
-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 2011-12-30T12:22:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/u-k-stocks-recoup-losses-leaving-ftse-100-index-little-changed.html
U.K. stocks recouped losses, leaving
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed. The gauge rose 0.1
percent to 5,570.37 as of 12:20 p.m. in  London , having earlier
fallen as much as 0.6 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
